data.description: Charming home located in gated community of Stonehaven with lake front AND cul-de-sac lot. Open floor plan has  eat-in kitchen which opens to family room. Spacious Master bedroom has his-and-her closets and sliding door to patio. Guest bathroom. Tile throughout home with wood floors in bedrooms. Fenced back patio and yard is perfect for pets, entertaining and relaxing.Plenty of storage! Community offers pool and tennis. Excellent location close to shopping, restaurants and major roads,and also 3 miles from beach!
